title: RIP LEAGUE
body: Login Queue is nice.... 7 day approximate login time. What happened Rito?{{sticker:slayer-jinx-unamused}} {{summoner:3}}

replies.body: Some service incidents happened last night that was preventing the login servers from working correctly. It was resolved a little later in the night before our scheduled maintenance started. If you still see issues or have any questions, let me know.
